reviewText: My kids love it!!! Would recommend.

My nine year old buddy in the children's program I teach loves the cartoon medley. I've not watched it myself, but it's one of his favorites. I was excited to find it in such good condition for a small price!
A must have. My 5 y/o and 2 y/o boys love this DVD. Very cute episodes. They watch it over and over. Great addition to their DVD collection.

My daughter loves Nick Jr. so it's no real surprise that she likes this video. I like having a small stock of CDs around so I can switch them out when she gets bored with one. Plus, if you have a car TV, they're great for that rotation too.
An excellent mix of educational shows for the preschooler.  My son adores it, and I love that he learns from it too.
